    12349 [label="ChooseALicense:\nThe University of Illinois/NCSA Open Source License, or UIUC license, is a\npermissive free software license, based on the <a href=\"/licenses/mit/\">MIT/X11\nlicense</a>  and the <a href=\"/licenses/bsd-3-clause/\">BSD 3-clause License</a>.\nIts conditions include requiring the preservation of copyright and license\nnotices both in source and in binary distributions and the prohibition of using\nthe names of the authors or the project organization to promote or endorse\nderived products."
